<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/misaka19092nd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242622); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3242622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1602924597" alt="Misaka19092nd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3242622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/misaka19092nd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3242622); return false;">Misaka19092nd</a></span></p>
